風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9a41239eb568ca049124c5f781b9bf5659839dd9","tid":1630681,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af419d2688eef87ee073286f21ed89f52d9a898a","tid":1630681,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb5ce08ecec3884acdde58d8c36e6ae4e3559c37","tid":1630681,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩長沙灣先有直升機低飛"}]}